data.text: Carol E. Boles Sterrett, 99, Indianapolis, passed away May 30, 2016. She is survived by two sons, Richard G. (Mariruth) Sterrett, Stephen E. (Lynn A.) Sterrett, three grandchildren, Lindsey Sterrett, Andrew Sterrett, Michael Sterrett, and one great grandchild, Mazin. Memorial contributions may be in her name to the charity of your choice. Visitation will be held Thursday from 10:30-11am at Flanner and Buchanan-Oaklawn Memorial Gardens (Conner Suite). Funeral services will be held there at 11am. Online condolences may be made at www.flannerbuchanan.com.
